  <span class="target" id="ecommerce-platform-fastspring"></span><div class="section" id="fastspring-store-integration">
<h1>FastSpring Store Integration<a class="headerlink" href="#fastspring-store-integration" title="Permalink to this headline">Â¶</a></h1>
<p>Curebit is easily integrated into your FastSpring store.</p>
<ol class="arabic">
<li><p class="first">Login to your FastSpring administration console with your administrator account.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Under <strong>Tracking</strong>, click on <strong>External Tracking</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Under <strong>Actions</strong>, click <strong>Add Custom Tracking Method</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Enter <em>&#8220;Curebit&#8221;</em> for Name, and under <strong>URL Type</strong>, select <em>&#8220;Free-form XHTML Fragment&#8221;</em>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">In the <em>&#8220;Free-form XHTML Fragment&#8221;</em> text area, put this code:</p>
<div class="admonition note">
<p class="first admonition-title">Note</p>
<p class="last">To get your personal integration code, YOUR-TALKABLE-SITE-ID needs to be
replaced with your Talkable Site ID. You can get this from your Talkable
dashboard after you log in and create a site.</p>
</div>
<div class="highlight-html"><div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>&lt;!-- Begin Curebit integration code --&gt;
&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;
  &lt;![CDATA[
    var curebitSiteId = &#39;YOUR-TALKABLE-SITE-ID&#39;;
    var curebitJsUrl = &#39;https://www.talkable.com/public/&#39; + curebitSiteId + &#39;/purchases/create_fastspring.js&#39;;
    var curebitVersion = &#39;0.2&#39;;
    var curebitOrderNumber = &quot;#{order.reference}&quot;;

    var curebitI = 0;
    var curebitItems = &#39;&#39;;
  ]]&gt;

  &lt;repeat value=&quot;#{order.allItems}&quot; var=&quot;orderItem&quot;&gt;
    &lt;![CDATA[
      curebitItems += &#39;purchase[items_attributes][&#39; + curebitI + &#39;][product_id]=&#39; + &#39;#{orderItem.productName}&#39; + &#39;&amp;&#39;;
      curebitItems += &#39;purchase[items_attributes][&#39; + curebitI + &#39;][price]=&#39; + &#39;#{orderItem.priceTotal.value}&#39; + &#39;&amp;&#39;;
      curebitItems += &#39;purchase[items_attributes][&#39; + curebitI + &#39;][quantity]=&#39; + &#39;#{orderItem.quantity}&#39; + &#39;&amp;&#39;;
      curebitI++;
    ]]&gt;
  &lt;/repeat&gt;

  &lt;![CDATA[
    var curebitJsSrc = curebitJsUrl +
      &#39;?v=&#39; + encodeURIComponent(curebitVersion) +
      &#39;&amp;purchase[order_number]=&#39; + curebitOrderNumber +
      &#39;&amp;purchase[subtotal]=&#39; + &#39;#{order.subTotal.value}&#39; +
      &#39;&amp;purchase[order_date]=&#39; + &#39;#{order.created}&#39; +
      &#39;&amp;purchase[email]=&#39; + &#39;#{order.customer.email}&#39; +
      &#39;&amp;&#39; + curebitItems;

    var curebitHeadID = document.getElementsByTagName(&#39;head&#39;)[0];
    var curebitNewScript = document.createElement(&#39;script&#39;);
    curebitNewScript.type = &#39;text/javascript&#39;;
    curebitNewScript.src = curebitJsSrc;
    curebitHeadID.appendChild(curebitNewScript);
  ]]&gt;
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;!-- End Curebit integration code --&gt;
</pre></div>
</div>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>Next</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Under <strong>Actions</strong>, click <strong>Save</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
